\eqn{\textbf{Q}}{Q} \tab\tab \eqn{rp \times rp}{rp x rp} state covariance matrix. The top \eqn{r \times r}{r x r} part gives the contemporaneous relationships, the rest are zeros by assumption 4.\cr\cr
